title: 3D.Live.Snooker.zip
description:
This game simulates snooker on your computer with full 3-D
environment and perfect 3Dd sound. It features easy and addictive
game play,supports short snooker(10 reds) and full snooker(15
reds) games.The balls roll just like real ones, and you can
position your cue shot to hit at various places on the cue ball
for different spins! 3D Live Snooker has single and multi-player
modes. You can play online or off.
